# Keep line endings stable across platforms.
#
# Windows CI runners default to core.autocrlf=true, which rewrites LF -> CRLF on
# checkout. That corrupts the byte-exact PCRE2 test corpora under testdata/ (each
# subject and expected value gains a trailing \r) and breaks the corpus tests.
# Pin the whole repo to LF, and treat the corpora as binary so no end-of-line
# translation is ever applied to them.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Byte-exact oracle data / golden corpora: never translate line endings.
testdata/** -text

# Binary assets.
*.png binary
